In anticipation of the Children’s Day celebration, Guardian Life is giving your kids the opportunity to get featured in the Spotlight page of our weekly magazine. To get your kids featured, follow the steps listed below:
• Write a post on why your kid deserves to be featured (not more than 100 words)
• Post a picture of your kid and caption it with what you have written
• Use the hashtag #GuardianLifeKidsSpecial also mention and tag @guardianlifeng on the post. A baby. Photo credit: Instagram/@nyirendajr Please Note!
– Applicants must be following @guardianlifeng on Instagram
– Shortlisted entries will be contacted via DM. Check out our Instagram, Facebook, and Twitter for more information.